text: Şehrazat Kemalî Söylemezoğlu (born September 3, 1952), known by her stage name Şehrazat or Şehro, is a well-known Turkish television personality, composer, songwriter, producer, and singer. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Turkish singers Category:Singer-songwriters Category:People from Ankara
title: Şehrazat
